{"title":"军中谣","authors":["张永枚"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"军中谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张永枚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨潇潇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连长去查哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着一捆绿树苗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边疆的土地湿茸茸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨所的战士正青春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好地方，好士兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连长啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云雨里进云雨里出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"查一哨，栽一树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下话儿种下苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春鸟儿叫道季节好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人快成长啊树苗快长高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜练"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑脸的陡岩扑面来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀的闪光是路灯光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头碰伤我的脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荆棘的手啊撕衣裳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像那大鹏爱长空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱白昼爱太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是为了我所爱呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱在黑地里练打仗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿公"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月下一河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一匹芦苇叶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔歌起，网儿开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿公的胡子月亮白。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水响，人影晃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌特藏刀袭边疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿公撩须头一昂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半空中张开银丝网；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿公袒胸把网拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边拉，一边骂："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这腥臭的鱼杂碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脏了月下一河水！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"网儿里鱼虾乱蹦跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"网儿里敌特嘴冒泡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿公押着敌人回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一跺脚敌人忙下跪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩头船桨挑渔网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿公说这是我的枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬月的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬月的阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照遍边疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的军营啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光做成的一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗户上，菜地里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射击场，阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光，阳光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬月的阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳在军徽上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳在自动枪口上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披着一身阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云上面开枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬月的阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边疆的春光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我亲爱的战士们哪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们就是那阳光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光似的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光似的心肠。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}